{"tid":2172304,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"德演唱會實驗 測試武肺傳播方式","createTime":"2020-08-24T13:32:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-24T13:44:49.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c065642191adfef8de23891c4c88860946dc75a6","tid":2172304,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T13:32:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200824/BIH7L4ISXVCJBCI732AOCBPOK4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200824%2FBIH7L4ISXVCJBCI732AOCBPOK4%2F&d=HUgUlm9NWlnA9xfyBh3SbpugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=0e3fe263\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200824%2FBIH7L4ISXVCJBCI732AOCBPOK4%2F&h=6556a42a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200824/BIH7L4ISXVCJBCI732AOCBPOK4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n德演唱會實驗 測試武肺傳播方式<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/2C7VE6toQtjeNmdAvll9yP8LrTU=/960x720/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2XW46ESC3BAD3AVPUF4VGAI4XA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F2C7VE6toQtjeNmdAvll9yP8LrTU%3D%2F960x720%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2XW46ESC3BAD3AVPUF4VGAI4XA.jpg&h=8b5e1964&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■參與演唱會實驗的觀眾都要戴口罩。<br />\n<br />\n德國哈雷大學醫院前天透過在。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n約1,500名實驗參與者前天入場，他們觀看流行歌手本茨科（Tim Bendzko）的表演前，已通過武漢肺炎病毒測試，全程也戴上口罩。研究員舉行的三場演唱會，分別模擬三個場境，先是疫情前期全無防護措施的情況、接着是採取了部份衞生防護措施，最後再把觀眾人數減半，模擬嚴格執行每人相隔1.5米的限制。為記錄現場數據，每位參加者身上都掛着接觸追蹤器，記錄他們在場館走過的路線、停留的地方和時間。他們又獲發螢光搓手液，來記錄他們碰觸過的表面，讓研究員得知最多人接觸的地方。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n增2,034確診近月新高<br />\n<br />\n德國近日新增個案數字再有上升趨勢，前天單日新增了2,034宗，是4月以來最高。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社"},{"pid":"3332b1b53d2ca2f5d12ec5273fcfef28c17d9d24","tid":2172304,"uid":175930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T13:36:05.000Z","msg":"癲過支那 玩活體實驗"},{"pid":"b13c3f0c93c32448a2f521fb7966e7295036c23a","tid":2172304,"uid":54946,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3332b1b53d2ca2f5d12ec5273fcfef28c17d9d24","tid":2172304,"uid":175930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T13:36:05.000Z","msg":"癲過支那 玩活體實驗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T13:44:49.000Z","msg":"自願有幾癲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}